International Summary

As of Wednesday, August 5, 2020, the total number of confirmed cases worldwide is 20,300,000.

The total number of deaths is 844,000.

The number of reported recoveries is 12,200,000.

The overall mortality rate based on reported deaths and confirmed cases is 4%.
